top_questions.text: Which data type is also known as logical data type in MS-Access?
Which query is used to make changes in data stored in the database?

Write down the output of the given program (Show with a dry run table). [3] DECLARE SUB SHOW(A) CLS N = 87 CALL SHOW(N) END SUB SHOW (A). DO B = A MOD 6 + 3 IF B MOD 4 = 0 THEN GOTO AA PRINT B; AA: A = A - 10 LOOP WHILE A >= 50 END SUB
